## VuePress {#vuepress-1 .text_wrapper__i87JK .mdx-components_mdx-heading__HweOA data-version="v1" style="--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--text-size:2rem;--text-line-height:2.5rem;--text-letter-spacing:-0.049375rem;--text-weight:600"}

This directory is a brief example of a
[VuePress](https://vuepress.vuejs.org/){.link_link__hbWKh
.link_highlight__kJZF9 rel="nofollow" target="_blank" zone="null"} site
that can be deployed to Vercel with zero-configuration.

### Deploy Your Own {#deploy-your-own .text_wrapper__i87JK .mdx-components_mdx-heading__HweOA data-version="v1" style="--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--text-size:1.5rem;--text-line-height:2rem;--text-letter-spacing:-0.029375rem;--text-weight:600"}

[](https://vercel.com/new/clone?repository-url=https://github.com/vercel/examples/tree/main/framework-boilerplates/vuepress&template=vuepress){.link_link__hbWKh
.link_highlight__kJZF9 rel="nofollow" target="_blank" zone="null"}

*Live Example:
[https://vuepress-starter-template.vercel.app](https://vuepress-starter-template.vercel.app){.link_link__hbWKh
.link_highlight__kJZF9 rel="nofollow" target="_blank" zone="null"}*

### Setup {#setup .text_wrapper__i87JK .mdx-components_mdx-heading__HweOA data-version="v1" style="--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--text-size:1.5rem;--text-line-height:2rem;--text-letter-spacing:-0.029375rem;--text-weight:600"}

Install the dependencies:

``` {.inline_code__cgX1y geist-inline-code="" data-version="v1"}
$ yarn install
```

#### Development {#development .text_wrapper__i87JK .mdx-components_mdx-heading__HweOA data-version="v1" style="--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--text-size:1.25rem;--text-line-height:1.5rem;--text-letter-spacing:-0.020625rem;--text-weight:600"}

Start the development server

``` {.inline_code__cgX1y geist-inline-code="" data-version="v1"}
$ yarn dev
```

#### Build the project {#build-the-project .text_wrapper__i87JK .mdx-components_mdx-heading__HweOA data-version="v1" style="--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--text-size:1.25rem;--text-line-height:1.5rem;--text-letter-spacing:-0.020625rem;--text-weight:600"}

Build for production

``` {.inline_code__cgX1y geist-inline-code="" data-version="v1"}
$ yarn build
```

#### Deploy {#deploy .text_wrapper__i87JK .mdx-components_mdx-heading__HweOA data-version="v1" style="--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--text-size:1.25rem;--text-line-height:1.5rem;--text-letter-spacing:-0.020625rem;--text-weight:600"}

Deploy your VuePress application to Vercel

``` {.inline_code__cgX1y geist-inline-code="" data-version="v1"}
$ vercel
```
